an><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >会议内容：</span><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:150%; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >为何要进行旅游标准化？</span><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >在加快转变发展方式，调整产业结构，推进旅游业转型升级的进程中，旅游业正从追求增长速度向速度与效益并重，从追求规模扩张向追求规模与质量并举，从重视硬件设施向硬件软件并重、重在软件提升的内涵式发展方式转变。开展旅游标准化试点工作，制定和落实涵盖各个旅游领域的旅游标准，加快搭建旅游标准化平台，有利于促进旅游产业结构的优化调整，推动旅游产业的提档升级；有利于规范旅游市场主体行为，催化企业发展内生机制，提高核心竞争力；有利于塑造知名品牌，促进旅游业向产业化、品牌化、特色化方向发展；有利于保护资源、环境与消费者利益，构建和谐社会，促进旅游业可持续发展。因此，坚持以科学发展观为指导，加快旅游业发展方式转变，推进旅游业转型升级，需要以标准化建设为突破口，在加快发展中推动转变，在加快转变中更好发展。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化的意义</span><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游企业发展的需要</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >如今旅游企业的竞争主要是接待服务质量的竞争，提高服务质量的关键之一在于服务质量的标准化，即建立企业服务质量等级标准，确立企业服务等级形象，并依照服务质量标准建立相应的质量管理质量评价和质量监控体系。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >培训和完善旅游市场体系的需要</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游市场秩序更多地需要依靠市场规则来维护，服务质量标准就是一种市场规则。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >促进旅游业全面与国际接轨的要求</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:21.4200pt; text-indent:-0.1000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化工作的重要功能之一是通过标准的制定，把国际惯例国际标准或国外先进标准吸收到我国旅游标准体系中，通过标准的实施，将这些国际通行作法运用到我国旅游行业，促进旅游业与国际接轨。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >4、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >保护旅游消费者合法权益的需要</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化是旅游服务质量管理的重要内容，旅游服务质量标准是处理旅游投诉的根本依据，开展旅游标准化工作也是保护旅游消费者合法权益的重要内容。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:150%; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化的步骤</span><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:150%; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准的制定</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >一般是通过调查研究有关的</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><a href=3D"http://wiki.mbalib.com/wiki/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE"  title=3D"技术数据" >技术数据</a></span>和<span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><a href=3D"http://wiki.mbalib.com/wiki/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99"  title=3D"统计资料" >统计资料</a></span>，比较和借鉴国际标准和国内外先进标准，经过认真分析研究而形成旅游标准草案；然后广泛征求各方面的意见和建议，对旅游标准草案进行修改和完善；最后，将形成的正式标准呈报有关部门审批后正式颁发和实施。&nbsp;<span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp17  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:150%; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准的执行</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准的贯彻和实施，是根据颁发的旅游技术标准、服务标准和管理标准，在旅游活动组织、服务提供和旅游管理中具体运用与落实。旅游标准的执行，一方面必须严格按照标准的规定和要求，在各项工作中贯彻落实；另一方面，在执行中出现问题时，应及时正确地进行协调处理，对无法处理的问题应尽快向旅游标准颁发部门报告和反馈，并且提出如何解决和改进的意见与建议，以便对旅游标准进行修订和完善。&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp17  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:150%; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3）</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准的管理</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化工作对于加强</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><a href=3D"http://wiki.mbalib.com/wiki/%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86"  title=3D"旅游管理" >旅游管理</a></span>是十分重要的，因此必须把标准化工作摆在重要的地位，成立标准化管理部门，指定专门人员负责，制定相应的<span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><a href=3D"http://wiki.mbalib.com/wiki/%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6"  title=3D"管理制度" >管理制度</a></span>和措施，切实抓好旅游标准的执行、检查、监督和管理等工作，以保证旅游标准的贯彻落实，提高实施旅游标准的效果。<span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游标准化管理的规划目标</span><span style=3D"font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >市场导向与政府推动相结合</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。适应市场需要，突出旅游企业主体地位，充分发挥政府的宏观指导和政策导向作用，加强组织领导和政策保障，创新标准化工作机制，形成政府部门、行业协会、相关企业、科研院所、中介机构共同推进旅游标准化工作的合力。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:18.0000pt; text-indent:-18.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:22.0000pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2、&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >重点突破与整体提升相结合</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >。推进旅游标准化工作应与</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >国内</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅游强国建设紧密结合，要围绕旅游业发展的中一心工作，重点加强基础性标准、行业急需标准以及涉及新型业态旅游产品标准的建设，并逐步向涉及旅游发展各基础要素的服务、管理、技术等标准领域拓展，以推动旅游标准化工作的整体提升。</span><span style=3D"font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-l